Citation.sTitle: Viscosities and Densities of Binary Mixtures of Hexane with 1-Chlorohexane between 293.15 K and 333.15 K
Citation.sAbstract: The density and viscosity values of binary mixtures of hexane with 1-chlorohexane have been measured as a function of composition and temperatures between 293.15 K and 333.15 K. The estimated uncertainties are less than 11 W 10-4 g7cm-3 for density and 10.5% for viscosity. Viscosity deviations  were fitted by the Redlich-Kister equation.
